node.text: The photo is sweet. Good stuff.

[Haus Brew SG] - Thanks to @hausbrew.sg I can quench my thirst with their differently flavoured milk tea and fruit tea. With the island wide delivery I can satisfy my thirst without stepping out of the house during the CB period.
The photo is sweet. Good stuff.
